medicaid to finance an 18000amonth apartment in manhattans 
trump tower a 5 million lakefront mansion in boca raton fla 
yachts and a fleet of custom cars 
this reverse robin hood has finally gotten his just 
desserts he said 
at the trial in state supreme court prosecutors charged that 
weinberg and his sons falsely billed medicaid by submitting phony 
reimbursement claims for about 400000 phony patients 
weinberg failed to appear at his jan 10 sentencing this year 
