good start in the right direction he added 
boucher declined to discuss elements of the plan which includes 
the rehabilitation of some 300000 palestinians living in refugee 
camps 
the united states views the elections as the centerpiece of the 
israeli plan but arens appeared to be trying to shift some of the 
emphasis away from the controversial election proposal to the 
rehabilitation idea 
