of the vote in a moscow district both men have become famous 
throughout the country for their investigation of corruption in 
uzbekistan that led to convictions of top local officials and led 
to yuri churbanov the soninlaw of former president leonid i 
brezhnev 
churbanov was convicted of taking bribes in december and 
sentenced to 12 year in a labor camp 
the commissions statement was read on the evening tv news 
program vremya ensuring that millions of soviets would hear it 
