the park manager who thinks he is independent of surrounding 
lands is living in a fantasy land 
agee said the goal in any future policies should not be to allow 
natural fires to burn for their own sake but to achieve natural 
changes in landscapes 
agee a fire resource management expert was a featured speaker 
