a total of 11113 credentialed teachers showed up friday 
including 8660 regular teachers and 2453 substitutes normally 
there are 26250 teachers 
the united teacherslos angeles union and the los angeles 
unified school district continued talks under a news blackout 
imposed by a state mediator 
at this point im cautiously optimistic that maybe we can move 
forward i hope those hopes are not dashed this afternoon at the 
meeting said utla president wayne johnson at a downtown rally 
that drew about 2000 strikers 
with student attendance nearly cut in half cafeteria workers 
face a nearly impossible game of guessing how much food to prepare 
each day the result has been considerable waste 
only 112 of the districts 573 school kitchens have signed up 
for a program to donate unused food to various agencies said carol 
noelting deputy director of the food services branch 
we did another mailing to the schools recently to see if we 
could drum up more business she said 
the utla represents 22000 of the districts 32000 teachers 
counselors nurses and librarians 
some strikers have applied in the adjacent districts of 
alhambra arcadia la canada and south pasadena but none have 
been hired 
since the disclosure wednesday that the state will enjoy a 25 
billion tax surplus over the next two years several wage offers 
have been made 
johnson said he was confident some of the surplus would go to 
the los angeles school district under proposition 98 which 
designates for public schools virtually all surplus funds above a 
certain expenditure limit 
he said the union would like a threeyear contract with a 26 
percent raise including a 10 percent raise the first year 
the district said it could not sweeten its 215 percent offer 
over three years until it was sure it had the funds but offered a 
contingency wage package of 24 percent over three years if it did 
receive some of the money 
the strike is the districts first since a 23day walkout in 
1970 
currently teachers annually earn from 23440 in beginning pay 
to 43319 to those with doctorates 98 extra course units and 19 
years experience 
