with kmg main hurdman two years ago into a firm called kpmg 
according to the atlantabased newsletter bowmans accounting 
report kpmg was the worlds largest accounting firm in at 39 
billion in world revenue in 1988 while arthur andersen was the 
biggest us accounting firm at 171 billion 
ernst amp whinney posted 219 billion in world revenue and 117 
billion in us revenue last year while arthur young had 205 
billion in world revenue and 843 million in us revenue bowmans 
stated 
